<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 9. Hylomus solenophorus sp. nov., holotype (IEBR-Myr 712 H) left gonopod, lateral view (A), mesal view (B) co = coxite, pref = prefemorite, fe = femorite, sl = solenomere, sph = solenophore, sg = seminal groove, k = distoapical process k. Scale bar: 1 mm." , "Figure 7. Hylomus solenophorus sp. nov., holotype (IEBR-Myr 712 H) segments 8 - 10, dorsal view (A, B); posteriormost segments, dorsal view (C); telson, ventral view (D)." , "Figure 6. Hylomus solenophorus sp. nov., holotype (IEBR-Myr 712 H) anteriormost body segments, dorsal view (A), lateral view (B) head, anterior view (C, D)." , "Figure 8. Hylomus solenophorus sp. nov., holotype (IEBR-Myr 712 H) sternal process between coxae 4, subventral view, normal light (A), UV light (B) gonopods, ventral view, normal light (C), UV light (D)." , "Figure 10. Hylomus solenophorus sp. nov., holotype (IEBR-Myr 712 H) left gonopod, ventral view (A), lateral view (B), mesal view (C) postfemoral region, mesal view (D) tip of gonopod, ventral view (E) sl = solenomere, sph = solenophore, k = distoapical process k. Scale bars: 100 μm (A-C, E); 40 μm (D)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/532203" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/532204" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/532201" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/532205" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/532202" .

